snippet.title: JUJUTSU KAISEN CURSED CLASH – Hidden Inventory/Premature Death DLC + FREE Update
snippet.description:
Master a new domain, now with new characters - Available May 30! Satoru Gojo (student), Suguru Geto (student), and Toji Fushiguro join the clash as part of Paid DLC Hidden Inventory/Premature Death. Plus, Mai Zen'in and Momo Nishimiya will join the fray in a FREE update!
